        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " and stood; at the side of him, or by him, putting his hands on him: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and said unto me, brother Saul; See Gill on Acts 9:17. ",
        "children": [
          {
